By inserting exactly 3 clock cycles of latency directly before, during, and after the arithmetic operation, the synthesis tool (Vivado) will perfectly absorb all registers into the `DSP48E2` primitive. This eliminates all fabric routing delays (since the signals never leave the silicon hard-macro), easily allowing operations up to 600+ MHz on UltraScale+.

